{
  "stem": "3658.1",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the whole thing was concentrated on your-- on dressing you up warmly.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Which was just as well, because we did need it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course-- So do you remember-- was it just your family went on that day, or were there--",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, the whole town, all of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We all went together to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The whole place, the whole town, we went.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The ghetto was-- first of all, they took us to a place in Irshava.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a big--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Bigger.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, next door to us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, you walked it in a half hour, just there it was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we couldn't go back home anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember some of them tried to run and get something, or they forgot, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were warning us not to go, because they can-- they'll catch us, and you can be in trouble.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They didn't say shoot, but you can be in big, big trouble.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But some people went back and they said the township was like a ghost town.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Nobody was there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was eerie.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And from there, the train-- there was a--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You went to the ghetto in Irshava.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, in Irshava.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then they took us to the ghetto in Munkacs, in Mukacevo.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's where we all went.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The whole town went there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "People not just from our town, but from all towns surrounding the area, in all the smaller towns, because Munkacs was a big, big city.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there's a huge Jewish community there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think more than half the people in Mukacevo, I believe, were Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they had this huge place, and very, very orthodox.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "One of the top of rabbis-- I don't know his name-- the whole world, even today, talks about him was in Munkacs.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
